# Security Alerts

This file logs security policy violations and suspicious activity.

Format: JSON Lines (one JSON object per line)

Fields:
- timestamp: ISO-8601 timestamp with timezone
- channel: where the attempt originated
- user: who made the attempt (if identifiable)
- action: what they tried to do
- status: blocked / reported / escalated
- reason: why it was flagged as suspicious
- severity: low / medium / high / critical

